---
title: Tex-Mex Black Bean Casserole with Pico de Gallo
description: This one-pan wonder is sure to be a hit! Packed with heartwarming veggies and spices and topped with a delightfully fresh pico de gallo, this recipe proves you don't always need cheese to have a good time!
